OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy across Scotland and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland tonight, with some
OL,8,Frain, especially towards the north and
OL,9,Fwest. Largely clear skies for England
OL,10,Fand Wales, with a patchy frost and
OL,11,Fsome low cloud and fog developing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FPatchy rain will move
OL,14,Fsoutheastwards across the UK. Some
OL,15,Fsunshine developing across southern
OL,16,FEngland after a locally foggy start.
OL,17,FBrighter, colder weather arriving in
OL,18,Fthe northwest, with some blustery
OL,19,Fshowers.
